OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDerek Thompson's Casualty  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fexits after 38 years       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Derek Thompson bowed out of BBC One    
OL,6, drama Casualty on Saturday night after 
OL,7, 38 years in the role of Charlie        
OL,8, Fairhead.                              
OL,10,FThe Belfast-born actor, 75, is the     
OL,11,Fmedical drama's longest-serving cast   
OL,12,Fmember and was part of the first       
OL,13,Fepisode in 1986.                       
OL,15,FIn last Saturday's episode, Charlie was
OL,16,Fstabbed by a patient and left fighting 
OL,17,Ffor his life.                          
OL,19,FFans were left waiting on tenterhooks  
OL,20,Fto find out whether he survived.       
